---
title: Ham, Cream Cheese and Tomato Baguette Serves 2
description: As much flavour as the beloved BLT, but with an exciting twist! Swapping lettuce for rocket and adding delicious cream cheese makes this easy-to-assemble lunch a real treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R5002_W37_IE_IEA28695-2_Main_high-1856b811.jpg
